00:09:21.950 --> 00:09:23.460
Huang Yu, kamu sungguh tidak berguna.

00:09:23.460 --> 00:09:25.630
Bagaimana kamu bisa begitu bingung?

00:09:27.880 --> 00:09:28.630
Tetapi

00:09:28.830 --> 00:09:29.900
afrodisiak

00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:31.620
sungguh ampuh.

00:09:31.710 --> 00:09:34.620
